short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Just pick up your ChatGPT Custom Instructions and go :)

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: My GPT CI's (Custom Instructions) is a Chrome extension that allows users to store and manage personalized instructions for ChatGPT to enhance interaction and response quality. The extension provides a simple interface to add, edit, pick, and delete custom instructions directly from your browser.
